MASTER-SAAO  robotic telescope (MASTER-Net: http://observ.pereplet.ru) 
located in SAAO was starting survey on the FERMI  GRB180810.28 error-box 
(ra=02 08 55 dec=-33 44 22 r=7.76)  50089 sec after notice time and 53011 
sec after trigger time at 2018-08-10 21:24:17 UT. The 5-sigma upper limit 
on our first (60s exposure)  set is about 19.7 mag


