https://196.21.94.34//master2/grb.php?not=2018-08-10+07%3A29%3A28.642038&sat=FERMI&gcrd=%2832.2292d%2C-33.7394d%29&eb=7.76&trig=2018-08-10+06%3A40%3A46.74&n=GRB180810.28


